snippet.title: Demigoddess! - 1st Trailer
snippet.description:
"Demigoddess!" is a unique game that focuses on the essentials of turn-based strategy games. It is designed so that each gameplay can be won or lost in approximately 1 hour. The game will be completed this winter!

Wishlist it on STEAM: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3281980/Demigoddess/
